<div type="definition">
<p>EXCESSIVELY FRUGAL.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. A4i 愛 refers to stinginess with respect to a certain item, or to a certain kind of items.</p>
<p>2. The negative quality of stinginess is lìn 吝 (ant. POST-BUDDHIST kāng kǎi 慷慨 "generous (with friends)", and in pre-Buddhist times the less exact huì 惠 "generous (to inferiors)").</p>
        </div>
